      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/dc386720-cdf0-11e4-bda9-5254006e85c2).  Ran 6 tests.  No failures.",
