        "subject": "LU-6383 ldlm: Improve debug for LDLM lock matching",
        "message": "LU-6383 ldlm: Improve debug for LDLM lock matching\n\nThe search_queue function is at the core of ldlm_lock\nmatching, and there is currently no debug output from\nit to track the lock matching process and indicate why\nlock matching failed.\n\nThis is extremely useful in debugging certain issues,\nsuch as LU-6368.\n\nThis patch adds debug in search_queue.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I8a7af6f119ab5425c2f4275e82cfd2241399857b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
